'''阿克薩戰士'''（{{lang-ar|جند الأقصى}}，Jund al-Aqsa）是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中的一個反政府武裝組織，奉行[[薩拉菲聖戰主義|薩拉菲聖戰主義]]。<ref name=Carnegie/>阿克薩戰士最初是恐怖組織[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]的一個下屬單位，<ref name=huffpo/>後來一度脫離，2016年10月重歸由努斯拉陣線改名的[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]。

==歷史==
2014年初，阿克薩戰士的成員大多數是非敘利亞籍的阿拉伯人戰士。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chechensinsyria.com/?p=20668|title=Another Split Among Chechen Jihadists over Fight with ISIS|publisher=From Chechnya to Syria|date=2014-03-04|accessdate=2015-04-07|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019103039/http://www.chechensinsyria.com/?p=20668|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到2014年底，阿克薩戰士已變成由敘利亞人佔多數，部分原因是一些人從其它反政府武裝團體脫離，轉投阿克薩戰士。<ref name=huffpo/>

2014年2月，阿克薩戰士攻佔瑪恩村，[[玛恩村屠杀|屠殺]]了超過21名阿拉維派平民。

2015年10月23日，阿克薩戰士脫離[[征服軍|征服軍]]，原因是不想與[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]對敵，不過阿克薩戰士仍然效忠[[基地组织|基地组织]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2015/11/al-qaeda-front-group-claims-success-in-key-syrian-town.php|title=Al Qaeda front group claims success in key Syrian town|publisher=Long War Journal|date=2015-11-05|accessdate=2015-11-08|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203103530/http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2015/11/al-qaeda-front-group-claims-success-in-key-syrian-town.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年2月17日，超過400名阿克薩戰士的成員與高層人員轉投[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]。<ref name="split"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/Charles_Lister/status/699989029769519104|title=Charles Lister|work=Twitter|date=2016-02-17|accessdate=2016-09-01|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222214830/https://twitter.com/Charles_Lister/status/699989029769519104|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年9月20日，美國國務院宣佈把阿克薩戰士列為恐怖組織。<ref name=xh20160922>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-09/22/c_129292134.htm |title=美国认定一叙武装为恐怖组织 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-09-22 |accessdate=2017-06-24 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713063649/http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2016-09/22/c_129292134.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年10月，阿克薩戰士與[[自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動|自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動]]在[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]境內的衝突加劇，在數個城鎮和村莊發生了其中一方驅趕另一方的事件。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-civil-war-boils-jihadists-trade-blows-hama-idlib/ |title=Jihadist civil war boils up as jihadists trade blows in Hama and Idlib |work=Al-Masdar News |date=2016-10-07 |accessdate=2016-10-12 |archive-date=2018-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181129185734/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-civil-war-boils-jihadists-trade-blows-hama-idlib/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在上述衝突期間，據報有800名武裝分子轉投阿克薩戰士，使得該組織的成員人數增至1,600人。<ref name=all>{{cite web |url=http://all4syria.info/Archive/351684 |title=Source: hundreds of fighters to leave their factions (Jund al-Aqsa) within two month |work=All4Syria |date=2016-10-07 |access-date=2016-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009164259/http://all4syria.info/Archive/351684 |archive-date=2016-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>同月阿克薩戰士宣稱效忠[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]。<ref name=extremist>{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syria-extremist-group-joins-al-qaida-affiliate/2016/10/09/d7e1c3a2-8e2d-11e6-bc00-1a9756d4111b_story.html?postshare=8021476045737245&tid=ss_tw |title=Syria extremist group joins al-Qaida affiliate |publisher=AP |date=2016-10-09 |accessdate=2016-10-09 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010212914/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syria-extremist-group-joins-al-qaida-affiliate/2016/10/09/d7e1c3a2-8e2d-11e6-bc00-1a9756d4111b_story.html?postshare=8021476045737245&tid=ss_tw |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年1月20日，盤據伊德利卜省的不同反對派團體再度爆發[[伊德利卜省衝突_(2017年)|武裝衝突]]。1月23日，征服沙姆陣線宣佈從其隊伍中驅逐親[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]的阿克薩戰士。<ref name=mee1>{{cite web|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/rebel-fighting-idlib-increases-tensions-over-peace-talks-2113068507|title=Syrian rebels threaten to 'annihilate' rivals as Idlib infighting rages|work=Middle East Eye|author=Alex MacDonald|date=2017-01-23|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124132455/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/rebel-fighting-idlib-increases-tensions-over-peace-talks-2113068507|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月7日，阿克薩戰士改名「'''阿克薩旅'''」。2月13日，阿克薩旅與由征服沙姆陣線及其它反對派團體組成的「[[沙姆解放組織|沙姆解放組織]]」在[[哈馬省|哈馬省]]北部及伊德利卜省南部爆發衝突。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2017/02/13/jihadist-rebel-groups-clash-in-northwest-syria--monitor/|title=Jihadist rebel groups clash in northwest Syria – monitor|work=Reuters|date=2017-02-13|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213120204/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2017/02/13/jihadist-rebel-groups-clash-in-northwest-syria--monitor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>沙姆解放組織向阿克薩旅宣戰，<ref name=ap>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syrian-state-media-says-talks-should-focus-on-terrorism/2017/02/14/079879a8-f29f-11e6-9fb1-2d8f3fc9c0ed_story.html?utm_term=.f57a7db4955d|title=Clashes between 2 extremist groups kill scores in Syria|work=Associated Press|author=Bassem Mroue|date=2017-02-14|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2017-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217223746/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syrian-state-media-says-talks-should-focus-on-terrorism/2017/02/14/079879a8-f29f-11e6-9fb1-2d8f3fc9c0ed_story.html?utm_term=.f57a7db4955d|dead-url=no}}</ref>並包圍在Khan Shaykhun鎮和Murak鎮的阿克薩旅武裝分子。<ref name="Jund al-Aqsa besieged">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jund-al-aqsa-completely-besieged-rival-rebel-factions-around-two-towns-idlib/|title=Jund al-Aqsa completely besieged by rival rebel factions around two towns in Idlib|author=Chris Tomson|work=al-Masdar News|date=2017-02-16|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216220414/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jund-al-aqsa-completely-besieged-rival-rebel-factions-around-two-towns-idlib/|dead-url=no}}</ref>沙姆解放組織和[[突厥斯坦伊斯兰党|突厥斯坦伊斯兰党]]其後同意讓阿克薩旅撤出敘利亞西北部，最後一批阿克薩旅成員在2月22日離開Khan Shaykhun，穿過敘政府軍控制區前往[[拉卡省|拉卡省]]加入[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]。<ref name="defect to ISIS">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/2000-radical-rebels-defect-isis-following-intra-rebel-deal/|title=Over 2,000 radical rebels defect to ISIS following intra-rebel deal|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=2017-02-23|publisher=|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603010011/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/2000-radical-rebels-defect-isis-following-intra-rebel-deal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>沙姆解放組織隨後宣佈阿克薩旅已經不再存在。<ref name="declare terminating">{{cite web|url=https://news.siteintelgroup.com/Jihadist-News/tahrir-al-sham-declare-terminating-liwa-al-aqsa.html|title=Tahrir al-Sham Declare Terminating Liwa al-Aqsa|first=|last=SITE|publisher=|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2019-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190117103211/https://news.siteintelgroup.com/Jihadist-News/tahrir-al-sham-declare-terminating-liwa-al-aqsa.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

